eplyTime":"2019-06-21T02:47:34.000Z","msg":"香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簽名數字不要低得難看啊！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=d4f5ad6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs</a><br />\n=====================================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山， 各位修行</span>"},{"pid":"21528ed006171d765dc57896a22ef676966fb461","tid":1246750,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"我諗耶穌寧願你哋冇聖經睇都唔好同魔鬼交易"},{"pid":"46f4cc8aec020fbaef8df541f58e959bdc2baafb","tid":1246750,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa97f0912ebe8e376bf0cd1f27b5c2f2dc238a9c","tid":1246750,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:46:51.000Z","msg":"聖經要成日買，唔係一本睇好耐架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"因為會有人新入教"},{"pid":"e230ed1f4204eccda515241b099489053009903f","tid":1246750,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bOfpxk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bOfpxk.png&h=42b211e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個app免費，有希伯來丶希臘文丶大量英文釋本丶中文丶阿拉伯文聖經都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /